'''Yohann Kouam''' (wavutse 1982), ni umukinnyi wa firime [[Ubufaransa|w’Abafaransa]] kimwe na producer, umwanditsi wa sinema ukomoka [[Kameruni|muri Kameruni.]]  Yakoze firime ngufi zamamaye cyane. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yohann numuyobozi wa firime y' [[ubufaransa]].  Se ni umucungamari naho nyina ni umunyamahoteri. 

== Umwuga ==
Yize gutunganya firime muri Institut des arts de diffusion  i Buruseli, hanyuma yiga Ubuhinduzi mu [[Bufaransa]].  Nyuma yaje kuba umufasha wigisha mumashuri yisumbuye gutanga amasomo yindimi. 

Muri 2007, Kouam yakoze film ngufi ''Fragments de vie'' . Yakiriwe neza, yakoze film ya kabiri ngufi ya ''Les dimanches de Léa'' mu 2010.  Yaje gukora filime ngufi ''Yagarutse'' mu 2013,  yamenyekanye ku rwego mpuzamahanga. Muri 2016, yakoze film ''Kuva San Francisco hamwe nUrukundo'' .

